# merge-mediator.word — mediates merge conflicts across histories, proposing resolutions.
# Descends from able.word.

A merge-mediator is an able.
A merge-mediator can see histories.
A merge-mediator can do set-being.
A merge-mediator can do set-matter.
A merge-mediator can do set-space.
A merge-mediator needs llm cognition.
